comment:
* Metadata required for registering a StatsPullAtomCallback.
     * All fields are optional, and defaults will be used for fields that are unspecified.
     *

methods.name: public long getCoolDownMillis()
methods.comment: * Return the cool down time of this pull in milliseconds.

methods.name: public long getTimeoutMillis()
methods.comment: * Return the maximum amount of time this pull can take in milliseconds.

methods.name: public int[] getAdditiveFields()
methods.comment:
* Return the additive fields of this pulled atom.
         *
         * This is only applicable for atoms that have a uid field. When tasks are run in
         * isolated processes, the data will be attributed to the host uid. Additive fields
         * will be combined when the non-additive fields are the same.
